From Mexico: Arsenal have identified PSV&rsquo;s Hirving Lozano as the perfect replacement for Alexis Sanchez (exclusive story by @CLMerlo)<br />
<br />
&ldquo;#AFC are prepared to make Lozano the most expensive Mexican player ever by offering &euro;48m for his signature.&rdquo;

Chinese Super League side Hebei CFFC have denied lodging a &pound;400,000-a-week offer for Arsenal star Alexis Sanchez.<br />
<br />
A senior club official told Southern Metropolis Daily: &quot;We have never made a bid or any offer for Sanchez. The Sun's story is fake news.&quot;
